Titolo: El Shaddai: Ascension of the Metatron

Anno: 2011

Descrizione: El Shaddai: Ascension of the Metatron is an action video game for the PlayStation 3 and Xbox 360 video game consoles. It is developed and published by UTV Ignition Games, a subsidiary of UTV Software Communications (who are owned by The Walt Disney Company India). The development was led by Sawaki Takeyasu, who had previously worked as an artist and character designer on Devil May Cry, ÅŒkami and Fatal Frame: Mask of the Lunar Eclipse. The game was released on April 28, 2011 in Japan, on August 16, 2011 in North America, and on September 9, 2011 in Europe. A port for Microsoft Windows was published by Crim in September 2021.A Nintendo Switch port is also in development.

Genere: Action 

Valutazione: 76
